{
  "texts": [
    "The methodology being explored intends to improve these training modules by proposing a novel technique for creating cyber exercise content.",
    "This strategy uses AI and machine learning technology to create situations that are detailed, technically sound, realistic, and imaginative.",
    "However, this research study's proposed framework AI-Assisted Cyber Exercise Content Generation Framework using Named Entity Recognition (AiCEF) has certain limitations, such as the need to expand the range of data sources, including threat intelligence reports and alerts, to enhance scenario generation within AiCEF.",
    "Moreover, refining the text synthesis mechanism to exclusively utilize cybersecurityspecific resources would improve the accuracy of technical terminologies.",
    "Additionally, the threat actor description component of AiCEF requires targeted enhancements to more effectively address the intricate dynamics of cybersecurity threats."
  ]
}